text: Ordered Char Siew with Roasted Pork rice...Char Siew was well roasted  with nice proportions of lean meat and fat. The Roasted Pork was also very good with nice crispy skin crackling even after having taken away home for an hour.  Adequate chili sauce with the right spice level.

The person at the counter is very rude!! When collected cash from me and return the change, he simply throw on the counter. The tall guy with both earrings on both ears behaves like he looks down on his customers. My goodness , what a way to do business.
The Roasted Duck is super 👍🏻👍🏻👍🏻 my children like the char Siew and roasted pork. The char Siew got bak kwa taste I like it too. Definitely will come back again!
Bought wonton mee from them today. The char siew given to me has barely any meat and mostly fats. Horrible.

The herbal duck is really good with the “aromatic lor”

Will come back again
